{"tid":2073779,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉慧卿：假如中央將港區國安法交回香港自行立法，才是「正確的路」。","createTime":"2020-06-21T14:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T15:04:27.000Z","uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"094f205bb189dc56cabd781d5eeebd62a5510a76","tid":2073779,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533173-20200620.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533173-20200620.htm&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y9T2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=ec1a18fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533173-20200620.htm&h=8ec4e0e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533173-20200620.htm</a><br />\n有政黨聯同英國國民海外護照（BNO）持有人，促請英國盡快落實擴大BNO持有人的權利，給予持有人居英權或英國公民身份。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨國際事務委員會主席劉慧卿表示，希望英國政府透過提供居英權予BNO持有人，讓港人知道有逃生門，能夠保障他們的權利。她又說，樂意看到全國人大常委會沒有在第一次會議時便立刻通過港區國安法草案，又說假如中央將港區國安法交回香港自行立法，才是「正確的路」。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨單仲偕說，以往草案大多要經過三次人大常委會會議才會通過，認為今次情況沒有例外。對於草案其中一項罪名是「勾結外國或者境外勢力」，與人大相關決定提到的「干預」字眼不同，單仲偕認為中央政府製造恐慌，也證明過往實行的一國兩制是徹底失敗，希望中央回頭是岸，撤回草案。"},{"pid":"bc7393b457a4e1fd2f2d9245fd1de33dcd9c9d51","tid":2073779,"uid":34065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:46:45.000Z","msg":"你咁撚鍾意國安國安 你都返支那啦 四方閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90f16fab9f37eaf7f25cf92cf0364b19b848fc1","tid":2073779,"uid":58789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"係唔撚好立呀"},{"pid":"b4f96327e209c83d1b92061c615d2659f52f3ce9","tid":2073779,"uid":318070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZwp0LK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZwp0LK.jpg&h=e738047f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://